item.title: Cute Pathan Kid Ahmad Shah memes
item.description: Origin A kid from Pakistan has recently become a viral sensation for his video. Watch the video here: His name is Ahmad Shah and some are calling him the cutest kid on the internet and I can’t disagree. üòç Sorry, Taimur. He has almost 200k likes on Facebook. He originally appeared in a viral video saying “Ye mera basta hai” (Translation: This is my bag) which then led to him appearing on national TV in Karachi on the show ‘Good Morning Pakistan’ on ARY Digital with Nida Yasir.
